<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes rather than fire primarily disturb this alliance. Most stands are open and rocky; however, fire could affect them in years in which introduced or native annuals form dense cover and sufficient flashy fuels. <i>Encelia virginensis </i> and <i>Viguiera reticulata </i>may sprout after fire or other disturbances.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
